author: Jordyn Tilchen
title: Sophie Turner Reveals What It’s Like Self-Isolating With ‘Social Butterfly’ Joe Jonas
description: Sophie Turner spoke to Conan O'Brien via video chat yesterday (March 31), where she revealed that she is 'loving' being in quarantine with husband Joe Jonas amid the coronavirus pandemic.
